'''John Gallagher''' is an artist who provided illustrations for some of the ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]'' sourcebooks. He also provided cover art for ''[[Star Wars: Republic]]'' [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] #79 and #80.

